		<td><b>Is It Legal To Make Hombrew NES Games?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So, I am brand new to this forum. I am wondering if it is legal to make homebrew NES games that DO NOT have any copyrighted material. In other words, the homebrew game content is purely original or draws from sources in the public domain?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

