	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Oh, that's right. I guess that's why some old unlicensed games were pretty creative about how they defeated the lockout mechanism - piggybacking the chip of an official cartridge, or simply provoke the console-side lockout chip to behave differently.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


